04)------WindowAggr: windowExpr=[[lag(stock_price.price) PARTITION BY [stock_price.company] ORDER BY [stock_price.price_date ASC NULLS LAST] ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING]]
05)--------Projection: stock_price.company, stock_price.price_date, stock_price.price, __mr_is_last_match_row
06)----------MatchRecognizePattern: partition_by=[stock_price.company] order_by=[stock_price.price_date ASC NULLS LAST] pattern=[A]
