01)Projection: stock_price.company, lag(stock_price.price) PARTITION BY [stock_price.company] ORDER BY [stock_price.price_date ASC NULLS LAST] ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING AS prev_price
