04)------WindowAggr: windowExpr=[[lag(stock_price.price) PARTITION BY [stock_price.company] ORDER BY [stock_price.price_date ASC NULLS LAST] ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING]]
